'Generality' may be: *The Assumption of Generality, a concept in psychology

A 'generality' or 'generalty' is a word used in Ancien Regime France and other
European countries of that era to indicate the regime of central government (as
opposed to a "particularity", which was the government of the provinces). These
include: *Generality (France) (généralité) *Generality (Netherlands)
(generaliteit) *Generality (Spain) (generalitat)
